I literally love this game. But there's something that I've noticed and this player needs to seriously be banned from ever acting this game again. His in game name is "IIAF" and recently I've been playing multiple matches with him/her. He always uses the f4d phantom from the regular gs3 package but he always glitches once you have a missle lock. He also can "outturn" ANY mig her in the game. As I recal, the f4 can turn with a mig if it has speed, but in his case, it doesn't matter, he won't even use afterburner and still keep up with the migs. He hacks and also used condescending language which disrupts the gameplay for the other players. He is a disgrace to the game a NEEDS TO BE BANNED FROM THE GAME. also, manny other renowned mig pilots share my concerns such as M.A.G.A and mig 17. Please do all of us pilots a favor and ban this malicious pilot from gs3. Thank you and have a nice day.
